{
  "content": [
    {
      "marker": "v",
      "number": "1",
      "sid": "TIT 1:1",
      "type": "verse",
    },
    "Paul, a ",
    {
      "content": [
        "servant",
      ],
      "marker": "bd",
      "type": "char",
    },
    " of God and an ",
    {
      "content": [
        "apostle",
      ],
      "marker": "bd",
      "type": "char",
    },
    " of Jesus Christ, for the faith of God's chosen people and the knowledge of the truth. ",
    {
      "marker": "v",
      "number": "2",
      "sid": "TIT 1:2",
      "type": "verse",
    },
    "These are in hope of eternal life that God, who does not lie, ",
    {
      "content": [
        "promised",
      ],
      "marker": "add",
      "type": "char",
    },
    " before all the ages of time. ",
    {
      "marker": "v",
      "number": "3",
      "sid": "TIT 1:3",
      "type": "verse",
    },
    "At the right time, he revealed his word by the message that he trusted me to deliver by the command of God our Savior.",
  ],
  "marker": "p",
  "type": "para",
}
`;

