    {
      "content": [
        {
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "7",
          "type": "verse",
        },
        "For the overseer must be blameless, as God's household manager.",
      ],
      "marker": "q1",
      "type": "para",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        "He must not be arrogant,",
