        "not addicted to wine,",
      ],
      "marker": "q2",
      "type": "para",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        "not a brawler,",
      ],
      "marker": "q2",
      "type": "para",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        "and not a greedy man.",
      ],
      "marker": "q2",
