      {
        "marker": "v",
        "number": "5",
        "type": "verse",
      },
      "For this purpose I left you in Crete, that you might set in order things not yet complete and ordain elders in every city as I directed you— ",
      {
        "marker": "v",
        "number": "6",
        "type": "verse",
